results.Name: Travel Backpack 45L
results.Description: A rugged, expandable, and brilliantly accessible carry-on travel backpack driven by a simple truth: No Two Trips Are The Same. Features top, side, front, and rear access via weatherproof UltraZips, meeting international carry-on size requirements. This backpack expands to a 45L gear-hauler and collapses to be a 35L day bag.

results.Name: Everyday Totepack
results.Description: Combines the clean look of a tote with the convenience of a backpack. Features padded straps, dual zip access points, FlexFold dividers, and dedicated laptop and tablet sleeves. Made from a 100% recycled 400D weatherproof shell.

results.Name: Everyday Backpack 30L
results.Description: Features weatherproof construction, expandable side pockets, and customizable FlexFold dividers. Designed to fit a laptop up to 15 inches, this pack includes external carry straps and multiple access points.
